  "title": "CONSTRUCTION SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Duties and Responsibilities </strong></u></p><ul><li>Ensuring teams work together to deliver quality work to strict deadlines.</li><li>Monitoring construction  processes, and providing training and team building sessions are required .</li><li>Ensuring adherence to health and safety regulations at all times.</li><li>Performing equipment material and routine site inspections.</li><li>Scheduling regular meetings with vendors, site inspectors managers and staff</li><li>Working closely with architects  and other professionals </li><li>Staying up to date with safety codes and advancements in construction</li><li>Assisting with the recruitment and training of new staff</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements: </strong></u></p><ul><li>Experience 07 (Seven) years in construction Sector.</li><li>Must agree to work on shift basis (Day/Night)</li><li>Must agree to work on Satur Day/SunDay/Public Holiday</li><li>Excellent communication skills</li><li>Ability to focus and keep calm under pressure </li><li>Expert in site Documentation & site work preparation </li></ul>",
